Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.87,0:02:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是外國的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏去島原必須搭船是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.62,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的劍士天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.09,0:02:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟比古師父約好\N一定要阻止他的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然是要去島原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果過世的兵衛說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這將導致\N許多無辜的島原人死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能置之不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為飛天御劍流第13任掌門\N也不能作視不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是我不願出馬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你這傻徒弟很有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.45,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把秘技都傳給你了\N你卻絲毫無意當第14代掌門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候不讓你勞動勞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.60,0:03:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數十年來\N讓你白吃白喝鍛練你就白費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有幾十年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你自己的決定 去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.55,0:03:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六十九話\N島原大戰一決雌雄的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.13,0:03:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都不曉得\N南蠻人比想像的矮小耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是娃娃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮的褲子 那是洋裝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的音樂盒耶\N哇 是玻璃珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.08,0:04:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 幹嘛大老遠\N帶這個鼬鼠姑娘過來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是翁爺爺的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.32,0:04:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他希望御庭番眾的情報網\N在這裏可以派上用場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那樣子是派不上用場啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們過來看 是蛋糕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？蛋糕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛋糕呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.93,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總督 非常的抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 誰叫你那麼慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.81,0:04:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了\N請問小弟弟有受傷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛爾思坦先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.36,0:04:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到緋村\N有這麼了不起的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村是我最感激的恩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕末時期我停留在長州時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.21,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時有股勢力排斥外國人\N我一度遭受暴徒攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.25,0:05:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時救我一命的人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在您擔任荷蘭的領事是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.82,0:05:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時愛爾思坦先生\N是熱心救人的醫學博士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是了不起的醫生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有關緋村先生的傳說\N我可是聽過無數次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來介紹\N這是我的左右手 山東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生 為何您要去島原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.75,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛爾思坦 我想問你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.25,0:05:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近島原一地\N有沒有什麼不對勁的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造反的謠言…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.06,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 您怎麼會如此猜測呢\N島原現在非常和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.64,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原確實有過\N鎮壓天主教的可悲歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是時代轉移到明治了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.44,0:06:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一派人鎮壓另一派人\N那種悲劇不可再重複
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.52,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 今後萬一\N島原地方有發生任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要連絡我\N我會盡所有力量來守護人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.70,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為熱愛民主主交的政治家\N虔誠的天主教徒 這是義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種氣氛拘謹的地方\N我最受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼幹這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了你 怎麼這麼暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.29,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話先講明 我頭一次碰到\N像你這麼高傲的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我是高傲的女人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.34,0:07:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有人這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕不原諒他…這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,項墜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.12,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我交給某個認識的人保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快就去拿回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不適合說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼久了一點也沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是個少女呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…聖母小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才我在那裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好清秀的花呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.06,0:08:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清秀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這散發出優雅清純的香味\N這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優雅清純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.61,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.58,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉傀王命令\N備好通往島原的船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王大人\N翔伍大人很快就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.41,0:09:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給生者血的祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血的祝福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人 翔伍大人回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.10,0:09:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來了 回來了 翔伍大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.25,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人 翔伍大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇跡呀 他創造奇跡了\N天空改變成黑色的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.53,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.17,0:10:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人創造的奇跡\N全部寫在這本預言書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天正元年\N南蠻人傳教師的預言書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時值明治 神子出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.18,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以上天賜予的力量\N創造了奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.88,0:10:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上天賜予的力量？奇跡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家看奇跡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.26,0:11:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是奇跡 翔伍大人創造奇跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.27,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見沒有 翔伍大人\N才是被神選上的奇跡之子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的救世主！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他掃除所有邪惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.01,0:11:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將把骯髒不堪的現世\N轉變成神的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.48,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 翔伍大人是救世主\N他會拯救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創造神的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.29,0:12:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人 翔伍大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.32,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都的復仇劇\N還是一樣那麼強烈鮮明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火炎的奇跡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王 那是你幹的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.93,0:13:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人們可是大受感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的救世主\N在海上創造火炎奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,治癒不治之癥\N白天也改變成黑夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都有為救世主\N捨命的覺悟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先講清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建設神的國度\N不須要耍假把戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你再動那些騙人的手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請大人原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山東傳來通報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊好像進入島原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.80,0:14:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒志志雄真實\N的傳說中的男人登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.41,0:14:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們建國的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他遲早會成為必需掃除的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最好的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.12,0:14:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.09,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你\N除了我任何人都無能殺掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要潛入島原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的\N按照兵衛留下的文書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍領導的勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已在附近\N準備建設秘密王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.58,0:14:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁今夜找出那個位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 你們加油\N我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.99,0:14:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說\N我有些御庭番眾的同伴在島原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去找他們搜集情報 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家 祝你們成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼬鼠丫頭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是前政府的密探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.28,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰跟禰彥在這裏等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.71,0:15:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到附近探索一下就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.82,0:15:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.33,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到有那麼多人會相信\N建設什麼王國、神國之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.77,0:15:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了明治時代\N才解除天主教禁令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原人們的悲傷\N不可能結束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只因他們信仰異國的神明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就奪走數不清的人們的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原人的悲傷\N不會就此結束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.35,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們背著幕府繼續偷偷祈禱\N相信救世主遲早會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個信心是他們唯一的救贖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.33,0:16:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你同情天草翔伍？\N認為他是救世主？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.47,0:16:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不瞭解\N總之我覺得很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去村子通知大家好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.68,0:16:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被發現是會被殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許他們知道\N有關天草翔伍的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.17,0:16:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外地人滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.78,0:16:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.05,0:16:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那些孩子的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 這些人逃得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.77,0:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰跑到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.14,0:18:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真驚人\N沒想到地面下有這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.34,0:18:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照兵衛留下的地圖\N地底下應該有隱藏的大教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大教堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.28,0:18:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是躲避德川幕府的監視\N天主教徒死守的秘密教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.92,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,250年前天草四郎禮拜的教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太難以相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.33,0:18:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真的存在\N幕府不會放過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.23,0:18:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道那到底是傳說\N還是真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對現在就要下地獄的人來說\N是什麼都不重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.65,0:19:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現了 這個魑魅魍魎\N正好 剛好給我牛刀小試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雞頭的 你就是拔刀齊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫相樂左之助 你記好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說那個小個子\N是出名的惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡魔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧 惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒完沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 快跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.11,0:20:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分成兩路\N回頭一次收拾一頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我天生具有\N受走狗喜歡的本質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.65,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我們的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放你活著回去\N我們會被全部殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.95,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部殺死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下地獄去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.05,0:22:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大教堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向神聖之名起誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心 我要燃燼你的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜將你獻上祭壇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.75,0:22:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害…

